#X text 554 216 cubic soft-clipper;
#X text 42 27 Let's forget about ploting tables now and just present the functions with pure math instead of table lookups. For soft clippers we've already seen 'tanh' and 'atan' \, which are well suited for soft clipping. These are available as thre first two modes of [drive~] (mode 0 and mode 1). For these modes \, the drive parameter is just a gain boost before reaching the waveshaper., f 61;
