#X text 520 71 The cubic soft clipper (mode 3) is a 3rd order polynomial that gradually rounds waveform peaks. The rational soft clipper (mode 4) uses a ratio of two expressions to progressively reduce gain as the signal grows. The exponential soft clipper uses an exponential curve that smoothly approaches a maximum output., f 67;
#X obj 778 319 drive~ -mode 4;
#X obj 654 571 drive~ -mode 5;
